snippet.textDisplay:
Mehrnigori Rustam is a popular Tajikistani singer. She was born on October 4, 1994, which would make her 31 years old in October 2025.
​Her songs include popular tracks like "Jodoogar," "Nigin Anar," "Dil Ay Dil," and "Guli Khushbu." She has also released albums such as DILI Zor and Jannati Ishq (both in 2023).
​She has recently released a number of singles, including a collaboration with Habib Wahid on "Moha Jadu | Coke Studio Bangla," as well as tracks like "Namichinam Guli Ke Khar Darad Dilbar," "Wada," and "Bosa" in 2025.
​In terms of upcoming performances, she is scheduled to perform with Fardin Faakhir in Switzerland on December 13, 2025, and in Frankfurt, Germany on December 27, 2025.
